description: Partial demolition, extension and refurbishment of buildings at 1 - 3 Buckingham Gate and 1 Palace Street (street block bounded by Stafford Place, Palace Street and Buckingham Gate), including excavation to form three basement levels, in connection with use of site as 78 residential units (Class C3) and a restaurant (Class A3) to the ground floor and part basement to the corner of Palace Street and Buckingham Gate.  Associated vehicular access from Palace Street, storage, plant, landscaping, basement parking and ancillary residential facilities.
